  "text": "Trying to improve aesthetic results, harvesting has been addressed in several ways, from shortening the scar to the endoscopic approach, with less traumatic tissue dissection and improved cosmesis [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] [CITATION_4] .",
